Unfortunately there are no translations into english for this title.
This is a Documentary where the life of this extraordinary artist Raul Seixas is told in a very respectful manner, just like he would deserve.

In the 60's and 70's re reshaped what was considered Brazilian POP music. One exemple is the song "Ouro de Tolo" (Fool's gold) which was a pre-RAP. This didn't exist back then.

Music was the trigger for me to start learning english. If you feel like doing the same towards portuguese, try translating this song first.
